{"tid":408050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街傳銷公司 各位小心屋企人受騙","createTime":"2017-09-21T02:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T17:12:39.000Z","uid":121305,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd83f6c65748b3225b827ae79c873daaab5388a","tid":408050,"uid":121305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"呢間叫H. E 活泉世界有限公司<br />\n話說我有2個屋企人經朋友介紹<br />\n飲左佢既21世紀精緻植物酵素濃縮液<br />\n成二千蚊一支 話就話台灣製造<br />\n但完全冇安全檢測嗰啲標籤<br />\n聲稱對身體有好多好處<br />\n俾人呃錢唔緊要<br />\n重點係我其中一個屋企人飲完之後<span style=\"color: red;\">瘋狂留鼻血</span><br />\n留到成隻杯咁多<br />\n另一個又作病 好似感冒咁<br />\n<br />\n呢啲傳銷真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一味掛住賺錢 唔理他人既健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附送2張垃圾產品圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/101013_4216c4de3d2b54830156b312fa814a01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F101013_4216c4de3d2b54830156b312fa814a01.jpg&h=fe30e8e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/101014_e5a697481abf0ea156aa07be45efcad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F101014_e5a697481abf0ea156aa07be45efcad4.jpg&h=85235a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都要小心身邊有冇人上當受騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e5a556309fc7d554f84e385f23185b1b3441fd","tid":408050,"uid":80928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"睇到啲成份狗都唔會想飲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}